'''Bavakar Medical Research Labs''' was a medical corporation operated by the [[Bavakar]]. The company existed during the latter part of the [[Old Sith Wars]]. It was considered to have been at the forefront of developmental [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetics]] research, developing a variety of medicines and cybernetic implants for personal use.

